{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·豳風·002.1", "text_original": "鴟鴞鴟鴞，既取我子，無毀我室！恩斯勤斯，鬻子之閔斯。", "text_normalized": "鴟鴞鴟鴞，既取我子，無毀我室！恩斯勤斯，鬻子之閔斯。", "notes": "鴟鴞 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·豳風·002.2", "text_original": "迨天之未陰雨，徹彼桑土。綢繆牖戶。今女下民，或敢侮予。", "text_normalized": "迨天之未陰雨，徹彼桑土。綢繆牖戶。今女下民，或敢侮予。", "notes": "鴟鴞 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·豳風·002.3", "text_original": "予手拮据，予所捋荼。予所蓄租，予口卒瘏。曰予未有室家。", "text_normalized": "予手拮据，予所捋荼。予所蓄租，予口卒瘏。曰予未有室家。", "notes": "鴟鴞 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-binfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·豳風·002.4", "text_original": "予羽譙譙，予尾翛翛。予室翹翹，風雨所漂搖。予維音嘵嘵。", "text_normalized": "予羽譙譙，予尾翛翛。予室翹翹，風雨所漂搖。予維音嘵嘵。", "notes": "鴟鴞 Chinese stanza 4."}
